<p><a name="Gothic_satire" id="Gothic_satire"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Gothic_fiction&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: Gothic satire">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Gothic satire</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Northanger_Abbey" title="Northanger Abbey">Northanger Abbey</a></i> (1818) by <a href="/wiki/Jane_Austen" title="Jane Austen">Jane Austen</a> <b>(<a href="http://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Northanger_Abbey" class="extiw" title="s:Northanger Abbey">Full text</a> at <a href="/wiki/Wikisource" title="Wikisource">Wikisource</a>)</b></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Nightmare_Abbey" title="Nightmare Abbey">Nightmare Abbey</a></i> (1818) by <a href="/wiki/Thomas_Love_Peacock" title="Thomas Love Peacock">Thomas Love Peacock</a> <b>(<a href="http://www.gutenberg.org/etext/9909" class="external text" title="http://www.gutenberg.org/etext/9909" rel="nofollow">Full text</a> at <a href="/wiki/Project_Gutenberg" title="Project Gutenberg">Project Gutenberg</a>)</b></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Ingoldsby_Legends" title="The Ingoldsby Legends">The Ingoldsby Legends</a></i> (1840) by <a href="/wiki/Thomas_Ingoldsby" title="Thomas Ingoldsby" class="mw-redirect">Thomas Ingoldsby</a> <b>(<a href="http://www.exclassics.com/ingold/ingintro.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.exclassics.com/ingold/ingintro.htm" rel="nofollow">Full text</a> at The Ex-Classics Website)</b></li>
</ul>
